    <TimeLineElement
      title="IMDT Technician"
      subtitle="From 2009 to 2013 at Technology and Systems Department, MINCOM, Havana, Cuba"
      desc="My first work was in a datacenter, involved maintaining and troubleshooting the hardware and software systems that store and process large amounts of data. As a specialist also perform tasks such as installing new equipment, configuring network settings, monitoring performance and security, and updating software. A datacenter I developed strong technical skills, problem-solving abilities, and attention to detail."
    />
    <TimeLineElement
      title="Network and Systems Administrator"
      subtitle="From 2013 to 2015 at Metropolitan Bank, attached to the Central Bank of Cuba, Havana, Cuba"
      desc="At the bank I was responsible for setting up, managing and troubleshooting the technology systems that the bank uses to operate and serve its customers. Also implement security measures to protect the bank's data and network from cyberattacks. And provide technical support to bank staff and help them use the software and hardware efficiently. Plus keep track of the technology costs and update the systems as needed."
    />
    <TimeLineElement
    title="General Systems Technician"
    subtitle="From 2015 to 2017 at Computer Emergency Response Team (CERT), MINCOM, Havana, Cuba"
    desc="As a specialist in a CERT I was responsible for responding to cyber incidents and providing technical support to prevent or mitigate cyber attacks. Performed tasks such as analyzing malware, conducting digital forensics, monitoring network traffic, managing security tools, and coordinating with other stakeholders."
    />
    <TimeLineElement
    title="IT and Communications Specialist"
    subtitle="From 2020 to present day at Wealth Management Company, OHC, Havana, Cuba"
    desc="I was responsible for creating and managing effective communication strategies that promote the company's services and brand image. Also handle internal and external communications, such as memos, newsletters, press releases, social media posts, and events. I worked closely with senior leadership, marketing professionals, and media outlets to ensure consistent and positive messaging across various platforms."
    />
